title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1725-1.3 - Management of housing companies
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1725-1.3 - Management of housing companies

State Regulations

This Chapter provides program, policy and technical
data and has as its prime objective the adoption and maintenance of proper
management standards for housing developments. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
1725-1.3

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
